Package gov.nih.nlm.meme.sql

Provides all classes for the MID-MEME object-relational mapping.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ActionEngine Generically represents a means of performing the various types of actions.
AtomMapper Maps a ResultSet to Atoms.
AttributeMapper Maps a ResultSet to Attributes.
ConceptMapper Maps the ResultSet to a Concept.
DataSourceConstants This interface holds constants commonly used by the MEME data source APIs.
DataWriter Generically represents a way of writing tables or queries from a database to a data file.
DataWriterHandler Generically represents a handler that pre-processes a line of data before it is written to a file
MEMEConnectionQueries This interface contains queries used by MEMEConnection.
MEMEDataSource Represents a connection to a source of MEME data.
MEMEScheduleListener Generically represents an application that listens for schedule events.
MIDDataSource Generically represents a connection to a source of MID data.
RelationshipMapper Maps a Relationship from a ResultSet.
ResultSetMapper Maps a ResultSet to an object.
 

Class Summary
ActionEngine.Default Reference ActionEngine imlementation.

AttributeMapper.Default Default implementation of AttributeMapper interface.
ConceptMapper.Default Default implementation of the ConceptMapper interface.

DataWriterConstraints Parameter container for the DataWriter.
EnhancedConnection Enhanced version of the Connection implementation in the java.sql package.
LongAttributeHandler Processes fields with "<>Long_Attribute<>:%' and looks up the long attribute values in stringtab.
LongAttributeMapper This mapping function assigns long attributes from the <>Long_Attribute<>: pointers in an Attribute.
MappingMapper This class contains overriden method of AttributeMapper.map(ResultSet, MEMEDataSource) to implement mappings of "XMAP", "XMAPTO" and "XMAPFROM" attributes.
MapSetMapper Represents a mechanism for creating a MapSet objects when concepts are being created.
MEMEConnection Generically represents a connection to a "MEME" database (MID or MRD).
MEMEDataSourceFactory Responsible for creating the "right" kind of MEMEDataSource based on structured set of properties.
MEMESchedule Used to spuport scheduling of MEME tasks.
MEMEScheduleEvent Indicates a change in the status of the schedule.
MeshEntryTermMapper Maps atoms to MeshEntryTerms.
MIDActionEngine Generically represents MID data source.
MIDConnection Represents a connection to a MID database.
MolecularActionQueryBuilder Builds a query for searching for molecular actions.
PreferredAtomMapper Maps the "related concept" of a relationship to the preferred atom.
QueryBuilder Builds query conditions from a search parameter list.
RelationshipMapper.Default This inner class serves as a default implementation of the RelationshipMapper interface.
ResultSetIterator Iterator over a ResultSet.
SemanticTypeQueryBuilder This dynamicaly builds an STY query from a list of SearchParameters.
SourceAtomMapper Maps a ResultSet to Atom.
SourceAttributeMapper Maps a ResultSet to an Attribute.
SourceRelationshipMapper Maps a ResultSet to a Relationship.
StringQueryBuilder Builds query conditions for string related parameters.
StripDuplicateSpacesHandler Removes duplicate spaces before sending a line of output to a file.
Ticket Parameter container class used to handle some configuration information for an editing session.
ValidatingActionEngine ActionEngine implementation that validates each MolecularAction after it is performed.
Version The Version class provides package version information for gov.nih.nlm.meme.sql package.
WordQueryBuilder Builds query conditions for word-based index lookups.
 

Package gov.nih.nlm.meme.sql Description

Provides all classes for the MID-MEME object-relational mapping. Basically,k it provides access to the database in the form of objects.
